               <msContents>
                  <summary>Psalter, ዳዊት፡, made in the Government Scriptorium. The midpoint of the Psalms is marked by a later hand in ink with the text "manfaqa Dawit."  Psalm 151 is the short version.  Song of Songs contains the scholars' version.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="5r" to="150r" facs="005">Fols 5r–150r</locus>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  <note><locus target="#99r" facs="099">Fol. 99r</locus> <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps118Spiritual"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2000Mazmur#Ps118Spiritual</span></ref> has the common, modern system of spiritual meanings of the Hebrew Letters</note>
